**Description**:  
Brought to you by Compukidmike, Redactd, Klipper, V0rtex, Mike's Wife, and BP.  
It takes a lot of people to make this happen! Badgelife is the best life. Come explore this crazy world of Badges. There will be something new and exciting this year!

